<h3>Attributes</h3>
The query attributes are:

<dl compact>
  <dt> <code>height</code>
  <dd> 
  <dt> <code>width</code>
  <dd> 
  <dt> <code>type</code>
  <dd> 
  <dt> <code>lw</code>
  <dd> line width, usually <em>height</em> * 0.15
  <dt> <code>bw</code>
  <dd> border width, usually 1
  <dt> <code>sp</code>
  <dd> character spacing, usually <em>height</em> * 0.1
</dl>

<h3>Types</h3>
The types are

<dl>
  <dt> <code>pia</code>
  <dd> ``PIA''
  <dt> <code>dofs</code>
  <dd> ``DOFS'' -- the ``S'' is particularly ugly
  <dt> <code>pent</code>
  <dd> The ``nested pentagons'' logo, unadorned.
  <dt> <code>logo</code>
  <dd> ``LOGO'' in typical style; admittedly a cheap shot.
</dl>

<h3>Bugs</h3>

<ul>
  <li> Eventually we may expand the types to include a complete alphabet.
  <li> The internal workings (in <code>PIA::Agents::Logo.pm</code>) are
       particularly revolting.<p>
</ul>

